    "Next, we explored the fine-tuning in Llama-7B.",
    "The performance metrics for the Llama fine-tuning models, as outlined in Table 3, indicate a range of effectiveness across different prompts.",
    "Specifically, prompts 1, 3 and 4 show the highest F1 scores at 0.600, accompanied by a recall of 0.500 and the highest precision of 0.750.",
    "The worst performance among the Llama fine-tuning models is for prompt 0, which has the lowest F1 score of 0.400 and recall of 0.286.",
    "However, its precision is relatively higher at 0.667."
